TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.STYLE_NUM, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.COLOR_CODE, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.ATTRIBUTION_CODE, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.SIZE_CODE, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.SEGMENT_ID, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.BUSINESS_SEG_DESC, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.STRATEGIC_BUSINESS_UNIT_DESC, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.DIVISION_GROUP_ID, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.DIVISION_GROUP, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.LOE_ID, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.LEVEL_OF_ENGAGEMENT, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.STYLE_GROUP_ID, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.STYLE_GROUP, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.FCST_SKU_KEY,
FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.PLACE_HOLDER, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.CUP_SIZE , FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.INVTY_CAP_GROUP, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.LCA_CODE, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.LCA_DESC, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.LCA_PRIORITY, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.LRP_STYLE, FCST_SKU_SALES_FORECAST_WEEK.FISCAL_YEAR, FCST_SKU_SALES_FORECAST_WEEK.FISCAL_PERIOD, FCST_SKU_SALES_FORECAST_WEEK.FISCAL_WEEK, FCST_SKU_SALES_FORECAST_WEEK.FORECAST_QUANTITY, FCST_ITEM_SKU.DIVISION_GROUP, FCST_ITEM_SKU.DIVISION_CODE, FCST_ITEM_SKU.ITEM_ID, FCST_SKU_SALES_FORECAST_WEEK.EVENT_QUANTITY,FCST_SKU_SALES_FORECAST_WEEK.IN_DC_DATE, FCST_SKU_SALES_FORECAST_WEEK.DEMAND_DRIVER,FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.INVENTORY_GROUP FROM FCST_SKU_SALES_FORECAST_WEEK FCST_SKU_SALES_FORECAST_WEEK JOIN FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT ON (FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.FCST_SKU_KEY=FCST_SKU_SALES_FORECAST_WEEK.FCST_SKU_KEY AND FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID=FCST_SKU_SALES_FORECAST_WEEK.BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID) JOIN FCST_ITEM_SKU FCST_ITEM_SKU ON (FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID = FCST_ITEM_SKU.BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID AND FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.FCST_SKU_KEY= FCST_ITEM_SKU.FCST_SKU_KEY) WHERE FCST_SKU_SALES_FORECAST_WEEK.FORECAST_TYPE = 'SHIPMENT' AND FCST_SKU_SALES_FORECAST_WEEK.FORECAST_QUANTITY <> 0 AND FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID NOT IN (SELECT PARAMETER_VALUE_NUMBER FROM HSF_BATCH.FCST_PARAMETERS WHERE PARAMETER_GROUP_NAME = 'IBP' AND PARAMETER_NAME LIKE 'SBU%')
